Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.70,0:00:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劍司 快躲開！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.98,0:01:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.48,0:01:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.88,0:01:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要放棄！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.75,0:01:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-劍司！\N-近藤！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.34,0:01:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼穹 - 天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.38,0:01:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙姬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.28,0:01:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.48,0:01:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.52,0:01:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是「痛楚」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.62,0:02:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,異界體！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.95,0:02:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙姬？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.06,0:02:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.59,0:02:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明已經下定決心了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.86,0:02:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.30,0:02:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙姬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.40,0:02:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.64,0:02:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.38,0:02:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,異界體 我就告訴你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.52,0:02:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所教你的戰鬥方法的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.12,0:02:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是消耗戰！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.72,0:02:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是要忍受痛楚的戰法！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.17,0:02:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是戰鬥的痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.07,0:02:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是存在的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.24,0:02:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是面對死亡的恐懼！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.07,0:02:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,異界體！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.58,0:03:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鶴…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.52,0:03:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.88,0:03:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要留在這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.95,0:03:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要留在這裡啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.09,0:03:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙姬 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.06,0:03:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 乙姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.07,0:03:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.44,0:03:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你逃不掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.65,0:03:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人的攻擊出現停滯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.39,0:03:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類軍陸續突破防衛線
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.23,0:03:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前進！別放過這個機會！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.46,0:03:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘可能不斷前進！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.24,0:03:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳 千鶴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.47,0:04:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.11,0:04:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要像是這樣變成這座島就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.62,0:04:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.32,0:04:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會擁抱住你們大家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.86,0:04:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是媽媽一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.43,0:04:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此我要和龍宮島合而為一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.71,0:04:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回歸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.28,0:04:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們回歸虛無吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.22,0:04:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家快散開！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.66,0:05:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要感謝自己還活著嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.90,0:05:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是存在於這裡的喜悅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.61,0:05:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,異界體…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.16,0:05:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…C地點…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.86,0:05:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.37,0:05:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠見 使用縛狼刃索
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.67,0:05:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.06,0:05:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是能讓人類跟異界體共存的資料
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.20,0:06:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也太多了吧 會超載的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.84,0:06:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 大部分都正傳送到別處
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.97,0:06:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.78,0:06:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍宮島？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.59,0:06:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.99,0:06:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北極傳來資料了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.36,0:06:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞爾維斯的所有伺服器及兀爾德之泉已自動接收
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.50,0:06:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是龐大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.60,0:06:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠超過之前接收的資料量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.31,0:06:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一騎他們已經抵達了紅音的意志跟希望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.81,0:06:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.11,0:06:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路線淨空
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.45,0:06:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有系統正常
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.38,0:06:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,導航系統正重新接收目標周邊的相關情報
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.12,0:06:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.32,0:06:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真壁紅音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.89,0:07:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經告訴絕望的我們 要我們活下去的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.91,0:07:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總士…就在裡面…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.22,0:07:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.16,0:07:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.60,0:07:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一騎…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.00,0:07:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有敵人！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.44,0:07:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不會…讓你們進去！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.59,0:08:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始進行核心的再同步作業
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.57,0:08:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.61,0:08:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說過禁止通行了嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.31,0:08:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你們搶走的東西還給我們吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.20,0:08:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一騎 不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.20,0:08:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要抵抗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.71,0:08:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…就是你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.71,0:08:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.75,0:09:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我…！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.63,0:09:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是敵方星核的騷動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.90,0:09:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一騎他…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.87,0:09:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把敵人的意識同化了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.37,0:09:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.74,0:09:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「接受」也是一種力量喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.05,0:09:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.82,0:09:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.97,0:09:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.94,0:10:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總士 你在那裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.71,0:10:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總士！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.58,0:10:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.78,0:10:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總士
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.59,0:10:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在吧 就在這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.69,0:10:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.99,0:10:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…還在這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.09,0:10:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆城
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.10,0:10:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總士
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.10,0:10:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.24,0:10:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一騎？你怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.31,0:10:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的眼睛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.37,0:10:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為同化的關係 肉體的同化現象復發了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.11,0:10:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.75,0:10:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.25,0:10:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要接受治療一定會康復的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.75,0:10:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.16,0:10:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到島上吧 一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.63,0:10:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:10:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星核…開始行動了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.40,0:11:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在 發射！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.27,0:11:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正前方出現敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.22,0:11:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙姬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.55,0:11:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後的同化開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.03,0:12:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-怎麼會這樣…\N-乙姬！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.74,0:12:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.08,0:12:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人的星核正想和天空連繫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.72,0:12:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它想要和大氣層外的異界體一起覆蓋住整個地球
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.12,0:12:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還來得及
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.46,0:12:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同化Mark VII武器攻擊它！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.09,0:12:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.46,0:12:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扳機由真矢來按
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.26,0:12:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.78,0:12:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將Mark Zein的能量用最大的功率釋放出去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.11,0:12:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機會只有一次而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.62,0:12:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多的話一騎的身體無法負荷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.79,0:13:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對它們來說 那或許是唯一的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.63,0:13:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此 也不是最後的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.03,0:13:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.32,0:13:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個星核也跟我一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.82,0:13:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了闡述生與死、存在與虛無是表裡合一不斷延續的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.79,0:13:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才會誕生在這個世界上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.03,0:13:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙姬 妳回去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.93,0:13:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到另一個星核的身邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.27,0:13:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.28,0:14:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,異界體…全都往下掉了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.18,0:14:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溝口先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.95,0:14:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認法夫那部隊所有駕駛員平安無事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.65,0:14:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辦到了 他們辦到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.67,0:14:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地底…起風了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.24,0:14:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,核心和島合而為一了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.54,0:14:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風…？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.98,0:14:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就在這裡喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.83,0:14:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家幹得好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.73,0:14:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就可以回去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.23,0:14:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一騎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.77,0:14:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mark Nicht！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.64,0:14:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.84,0:15:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星核用自己的死亡賦予異界體成為了個體
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.58,0:15:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再這樣下去會拖累所有的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.61,0:15:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.78,0:15:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一騎！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.22,0:15:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠見！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.49,0:15:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來 遠見！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.09,0:15:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…一定會…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.63,0:15:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.76,0:15:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一騎！一騎！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.27,0:15:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜下來！同步直接連結還沒中斷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.94,0:15:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要少了任何一人 同步連結就沒有作用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.61,0:15:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是妳在戰鬥之前告訴我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.91,0:15:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一騎…他還活著…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.29,0:15:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不存在於任何地方 存在於這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.93,0:15:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在與虛無正相互對抗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.27,0:16:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不存在於任何地方…存在於這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.17,0:16:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一騎…總士…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.68,0:16:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是將一切回歸虛無 來自異界體的祝福
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.05,0:16:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕在現實的世界中 我們的存在已經消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.59,0:16:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一騎…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.63,0:16:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.63,0:16:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們…還在這裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.73,0:16:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.33,0:16:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在這裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.28,0:16:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甲洋！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.39,0:17:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就在這裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.61,0:17:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.78,0:17:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是人類的宇宙艦隊以及大氣層外的異界體核心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.09,0:17:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙方都燃燒殆盡而墜落了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.39,0:17:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡 一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.16,0:17:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整艘艦艇在出發之前就被摧毀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.99,0:17:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是引擎仍然毫髮無傷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.16,0:17:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將機體的構造同化 把控制權交由系統管理
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.47,0:17:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起飛之後就由我來操縱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.71,0:17:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能飛嗎 一騎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.58,0:17:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然能飛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.24,0:17:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有我陪著你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.61,0:17:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.35,0:17:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.15,0:18:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星核理解生命的循環了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.39,0:18:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是乙姬嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.19,0:18:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 她本人是不可能再生的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.33,0:18:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那將只是複製出同樣的事物 違背了生命的本質
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.47,0:18:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經是乙姬的存在轉生成為新的事物了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.41,0:18:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼她終將成長為核心 並且能夠與我們對話的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.45,0:18:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我們把這座島當作希望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.05,0:18:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且繼續留在這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.69,0:18:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續直走就能回到島上了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.76,0:18:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到頭來還是你救了我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.13,0:18:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一騎 我教導異界體什麼是痛楚與存在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.14,0:18:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我也理解了他們的祝福
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.31,0:19:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理解了存在與虛無的循環
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.31,0:19:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在與虛無的循環？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.72,0:19:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.05,0:19:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的身體…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.42,0:19:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經幾乎不存在了 一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.26,0:19:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到島上一起接受治療吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.56,0:19:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此一來一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.93,0:19:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就這麼做吧 一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.50,0:19:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就要消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.10,0:19:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總士 你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.44,0:19:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再說了 總士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.11,0:19:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會到異界體那裡一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.68,0:19:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後再度創造出自己的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.28,0:19:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不知道會花上多久
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.12,0:19:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.26,0:19:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總士 你在吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.99,0:19:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那裡吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.70,0:19:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總士…總士！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.27,0:19:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.87,0:20:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到我們重逢為止…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.82,0:20:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總士！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.83,0:20:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mark VII的緊急修理完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.23,0:20:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨時都可以出動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.64,0:20:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.77,0:20:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛員的精神狀態也穩定了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.04,0:20:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.11,0:20:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開第七巨龍之洞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.58,0:20:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法夫那Mark VII 出動！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.39,0:00:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.39,0:00:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.39,0:00:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.05,0:21:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總士 我就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.39,0:21:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就在這裡等你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.39,0:22:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.39,0:00:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.36,0:21:02.35,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,{\fad(300,300)\fs20\be1}我可以懵懂無知吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.43,0:21:06.76,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,{\fad(300,300)\fs20\be1}眺望著夢想的痕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.90,0:21:16.81,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,{\fad(300,3000)\fs20\be1}再見了 湛藍的歲月
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.19,0:21:35.22,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,{\fad(300,300)\fs20\be1}即使將珍貴的事物當成跳板
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.26,0:21:41.32,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,{\fad(300,300)\fs20\be1}也想摘下最高處的蘋果
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.43,0:21:47.43,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,{\fad(300,300)\fs20\be1}失去了才察覺到值得尊崇的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.51,0:21:54.84,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,{\fad(300,1800)\fs20\be1}年幼的我們總是不得要領
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.51,0:21:59.45,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,{\fad(300,300)\fs20\be1}充盈於每一天的鎮壓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.55,0:22:02.64,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,{\fad(300,300)\fs20\be1}使得情緒變得不安定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.72,0:22:08.72,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,{\fad(300,300)\fs20\be1}即使受傷也祈禱能拍動羽翼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.86,0:22:15.19,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,{\fad(300,300)\fs20\be1}我可以懵懂無知吧 眺望著夢想的痕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.27,0:22:21.17,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,{\fad(300,1000)\fs20\be1}再見了 湛藍的歲月
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.45,0:22:33.36,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,{\fad(300,300)\fs20\be1}正因為保持距離 才能得知自由的份量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.46,0:22:39.73,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,{\fad(300,300)\fs20\be1}未成熟的心甚至無法理解這一點
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.87,0:22:45.96,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,{\fad(300,300)\fs20\be1}現在就敢如此斷言吧 這裡就是所謂的樂園
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.10,0:22:51.60,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,{\fad(300,1300)\fs20\be1}再見了 湛藍的歲月
